      "name": "Spear of Misery",
      "description": "Moskov launches a powerful strike at the target enemy hero or Creep, dealing 300( +60% Total Physical Attack) (Physical Damage), knocking them back, and revealing their position for 5s. If the target collides with an enemy hero when knocked back, they'll both take 200( +30% Total Physical Attack) (Physical Damage) and be stunned for 1.5s. If the enemy is knocked into a wall, they will also be stunned for the same duration.",
